1812
01:28:40,246 --> 01:28:43,116
Can we please? The implosion
device is nowhere.

1813
01:28:43,149 --> 01:28:44,551
Hey, you can't rush everything.

1814
01:28:44,584 --> 01:28:46,119
-Oppie, please.
-Well, there's rushing

