Wait. Neddermeyer's
doing his job.

1817
01:28:50,022 --> 01:28:50,956
Teller's not helping.

1818
01:28:50,989 --> 01:28:52,525
You're not helping.

1819
01:28:52,559 --> 01:28:53,959
I've been asking
for calculations

1820
