1821
01:28:55,161 --> 01:28:56,629
The British can do it. Fuchs.

1822
01:28:56,663 --> 01:28:57,963
Absolutely.

1823
01:28:57,996 --> 01:28:59,366
It's your job, Teller.

1824
01:28:59,399 --> 01:29:01,201
I'm engaged in research.

1825
01:29:01,234 --> 01:29:03,902
